{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e6a4b596e1","title":"给司徒美堂“的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"78b18fa584","index":0,"year":1949,"month":1,"day":20,"articleId":"e6a4b596e1"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji26","name":"毛泽东全集第26卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji26.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji26":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"488197c747","type":"paragraph","text":"给司徒美堂“的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji26","articleId":"e6a4b596e1"},{"id":"6c75b121fc","type":"paragraph","text":"（1949年1月20日）司徒美觉先生去年十月二十三日惠书，因交通阻模，今始获悉。热情卓见，感佩殊深。中国人民解放斗争日益接近全国胜利，召开新的政治协商会议，建立民主联合政府，团结全国人民及海外侨胞的力量，完全实现中国人民的独立解放事业，实为当务之急。为此，函待各民主党派各界民主人士共同商讨。至盼先生拼挡公务早日回国，花态解放区参加会议。如旅途尚需时日，亦析将筹备意见先行电示，以利进行。通电欢迎，并盼赐复","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji26","articleId":"e6a4b596e1"},{"id":"8b02dfce35","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji26","articleId":"e6a4b596e1"},{"id":"bcc0c4ab04","type":"paragraph","text":"一九四九年一月二十日[1]司徒美堂（1868-1955），广东开平人，爱国华侨领袖。曾任美洲致公党主座。1949年应邀回国参加中国人民政治协商会议第一届全体会议。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji26","articleId":"e6a4b596e1"}],"page":{"id":"5d2448e7f9","publicationId":"maoquanji26","articleId":"e6a4b596e1","start":38,"end":38}}}},"__N_SSG":true}